{"tid":2490980,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中環群眾抗議修例 警方事隔近年半起訴餐廳經理非法集結","createTime":"2021-04-16T04:02:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T06:15:07.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"80f2975c311d6f5682e4fbc3c2460dd47e6665ef","tid":2490980,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T04:02:05.000Z","msg":"網民前年11月發起三罷行動，連日在各區堵路示威。事隔一年多，警方拘捕一名餐廳經理，指稱他於「黎明行動」當日在中環參與非法集結，案件今在東區裁判法院提堂。主任裁判官羅德泉押後案件至6月8日再訊，待辯方索取文件及法律意見，並批准被告以1,000元保釋外出，惟其間不得離港，並須每周向警署報到。<br />\n<br />\n控罪指被告於前年11月11日在中環德輔道中與畢打街與其他不知名人士參與非法集結。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210416/533DTNWEJVEZ7DWZ5UJY5S64JM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210416%2F533DTNWEJVEZ7DWZ5UJY5S64JM%2F&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwEcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=2069a8e0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210416%2F533DTNWEJVEZ7DWZ5UJY5S64JM%2F&h=f7d56e05\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210416/533DTNWEJVEZ7DWZ5UJY5S64JM/</a>"},{"pid":"35855b5abd8e04fc2aecbb485aed58ded77121d3","tid":2490980,"uid":170949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T04:03:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"422fd5dfb879d3a8f6a749f64bb3bcae4ccd4d25","tid":2490980,"uid":87985,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T04:33:28.000Z","msg":"非集都唔畀離港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6586abf6222c23a292a08af7ca3d80daa360361d","tid":2490980,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T04:45:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" clas